## 📁 Project Structure

```
resume-ai-app/
├── app.py                  # Flask backend + all API routes
├── requirements.txt        # Python dependencies
├── Procfile                # Render/Railway deployment config
├── README.md               # This file
├── templates/
│   └── index.html          # Main HTML template (glassmorphism UI)
├── static/
│   ├── css/
│   │   └── style.css       # Full CSS (variables, glassmorphism, animations)
│   ├── js/
│   │   ├── app.js          # Frontend logic (upload, interview, scoring)
│   │   └── background3d.js # Three.js 3D scene
│   └── 3d/                 # (reserved for additional 3D assets)
└── uploads/                # Temporary PDF storage (auto-cleaned)
```

---

## 🌐 Deploy to Render (Free)

1. Push your code to GitHub
2. Go to [render.com](https://render.com) → New → Web Service
3. Connect your GitHub repo
4. Set these values:
   - **Build Command:** `pip install -r requirements.txt`
   - **Start Command:** `gunicorn app:app`
   - **Environment:** Python 3
5. Click **Create Web Service** — done! ✅

### Environment Variables (optional)
| Variable | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `SECRET_KEY` | `resume-ai-secret-key-2024` | Flask session secret |
| `PORT` | `5000` | Server port |
| `FLASK_ENV` | `development` | Set to `production` on deploy |

---

## 🎯 API Endpoints

| Method | Route | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/` | Main application page |
| `POST` | `/analyze` | Upload + analyze PDF resume |
| `POST` | `/demo-analyze` | Analyze with demo data |
| `POST` | `/interview/start` | Start interview session |
| `POST` | `/interview/answer` | Submit answer + get feedback |
| `GET` | `/interview/results` | Get final interview results |

---

## 💡 Tips for Best Results

- **Resume PDF**: Ensure your PDF is text-based (not a scanned image)
- **Skills**: List skills clearly in a dedicated section for better detection
- **Interview answers**: Aim for 80–150 words using the STAR method (Situation, Task, Action, Result)
- Use `Ctrl+Enter` to quickly submit interview answers

